Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,中午在外面吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.82,0:00:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 晚上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,每晚都是爛醉而歸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也是呢
